Hepatic encephalopathy. In: Sheila S, editor. Diseases of the liver and biliary system, 10th ed. Oxford: Blackwell Science Ltd.; 1996. p. 87-102. 
Fulminant hepatic failure. In: Sheila S, editor. Diseases of the liver and biliary system, 10th ed. Oxford: Blackwell Science Ltd.; 1996. p. 103-17.Fulminant hepatic failure. In: Schiff ER, editor. Diseases of the liver, 8th ed. New York: Lippincott-Raven Ltd.; 1999. p. 879-97.
